<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - GPT Adventure</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #16213e 100%);
            color: #00ff41;
            font-family: 'Courier New', 'Lucida Console', monospace;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 15px;
        }
        
        .navbar {
            background-color: #001100;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #00ff00;
            padding: 15px 0;
        }
        
        .navbar-brand {
            color: #00ff00 !important;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .nav-link {
            color: #00ff41 !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        
        .nav-link:hover {
            color: #00ff00 !important;
        }
        
        .navbar-nav {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            margin-left: auto;
        }
        
        .navbar-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .card {
            background-color: #001100;
            border: 2px solid #00ff00;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.2);
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .card-header {
            background-color: #002200;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #00ff00;
            padding: 15px 20px;
        }
        
        .card-header h2 {
            color: #00ff00;
            margin: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .card-body {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        h4 {
            color: #00ff00;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #00ff00;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0 15px 0;
        }
        
        ul, ol {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        li {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        
        strong {
            color: #00ff00;
        }
        
        .btn {
            background-color: #003300;
            color: #00ff00;
            border: 2px solid #00ff00;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-family: 'Courier New', 'Lucida Console', monospace;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #00ff00;
            color: #000000;
        }
        
        .row {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 0 -15px;
        }
        
        .col-md-8 {
            width: 66.666667%;
            padding: 0 15px;
        }
        
        .justify-content-center {
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .mt-5 {
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }
        
        .mt-4 {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .col-md-8 {
                width: 100%;
            }
            
            .navbar-content {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .navbar-nav {
                margin-left: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="navbar-content">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">GPT Adventure</a>
                <div class="navbar-nav">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
                    <% if (user) { %>
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h2>About GPT Adventure</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>GPT Adventure is an interactive text-based adventure game powered by OpenAI's GPT technology.</p>
                        
                        <h4>Features:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Multiple Game Modes:</strong> Fantasy Adventure, Sci-Fi, Mystery, and Custom worlds</li>
                            <li><strong>Interactive Compass:</strong> Visual exit map with clickable directions</li>
                            <li><strong>Location Images:</strong> AI-generated images for game locations</li>
                            <li><strong>Persistent Characters:</strong> Your character and progress are saved</li>
                            <li><strong>Dynamic Storytelling:</strong> AI adapts to your choices and creates unique narratives</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h4>How to Play:</h4>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Create an account or log in</li>
                            <li>Choose your adventure type from the dashboard</li>
                            <li>Create your character</li>
                            <li>Type commands like "look around", "go north", "attack goblin"</li>
                            <li>Use the compass to navigate by clicking on available exits</li>
                        </ol>

                        <p class="mt-4">
                            <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Start Your Adventure</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>